{
  "text": "For believers, complete and true devotion and obedience to God is a constant source of spiritual, emotional, and moral energy and is helpful in resisting destructive environmental attacks as well as social and mental disruption [CITATION_1] . For the past few decades, researchers have systematically investigated connections between religiosity and mental health and have identified a consistent relationship between them in adolescent populations [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] .",
